data.description: Come check out this GORGEOUS 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home in the Retreat at Bay Forest Subdivision. This gated neighborhood is the perfect hideaway!! This home offers 4 bedrooms, TWO primaries, one on the first floor, 3.5 bathrooms AND a gorgeous pool with a raised spa, and NO BACK NEIGHBORS!!!! You do not want to miss out on this one!! Call today for your private tour!!
